# Semgrep ignore patterns for TOON
#
# CWE-319 (Cleartext Transmission) false positives:
# The ws:// URLs in these files are for:
#   - Docker-internal container-to-container networking (no TLS needed)
#   - Validation checks (not actual connections)
#   - Test fixtures and examples
#   - Error message text and log output
#
# Production deployments use wss:// via Marlin Oyster CVM's
# vsock proxy which terminates TLS at the enclave boundary.

# Test files -- ws:// in test fixtures is never a real connection
**/*.test.ts
**/tests/**
**/__integration__/**

# Docker compose files -- container-internal networking
docker-compose-*.yml

# Deployment scripts -- internal network URLs
deploy-*.sh

# Examples -- developer reference code, not production
examples/
packages/examples/
